data.details: This transformative case features a 67-year-old female patient who sought to rejuvenate her appearance and boost her confidence. She underwent a breast lift using the anchor technique, which is ideal for achieving a significant lift and reshaping, particularly beneficial in cases of considerable sagging. Additionally, she received a tummy tuck to remove excess skin and tighten the abdominal area, which often becomes more pronounced with age and life changes. The before and after images illustrate a remarkable transformation. The breast lift has restored a youthful contour and firmness to her breasts, while the tummy tuck has resulted in a smoother, flatter abdomen, enhancing her overall body profile. These procedures together have not only improved her physical appearance but have also likely had a positive impact on her self-esteem and quality of life. This case exemplifies the advanced techniques and personalized care our practice offers to meet the unique needs of our mature patients.

This remarkable transformation showcases a 73-year-old female patient who underwent a facelift and neck lift using the advanced deep plane technique. The before image highlights visible signs of aging, including sagging skin and pronounced folds along the neck and jawline. Post-procedure, the after image reveals a rejuvenated appearance with a smoother, more contoured neck and a lifted, youthful facial structure. The deep plane technique allowed for a significant yet natural-looking lift, enhancing the patient's features while maintaining her natural expression. This case exemplifies our commitment to achieving age-defying results that respect the unique characteristics of each patient, providing a refreshed and revitalized look that radiates confidence.

This case features a 19-year-old female patient who sought to enhance her facial contours through liposuction. The before and after images illustrate the remarkable transformation achieved through targeted liposuction along the jawline and under the chin. This procedure was meticulously planned and executed to refine her natural features while maintaining a balanced and harmonious facial appearance. The after photo, taken several weeks post-procedure, showcases a more defined jawline and a subtly sculpted profile, contributing to an overall rejuvenated and confident look. This case highlights the precision and artistry involved in facial contouring surgeries, demonstrating our commitment to achieving natural and aesthetically pleasing results tailored to each patient's unique desires.
Tummy tuck (abdominoplasty) performed to remove excess skin and tighten abdominal muscles, resulting in a flatter, firmer abdominal contour.
Liposuction of the abdomen and flanks performed to remove excess fat deposits and enhance body contour for a slimmer, more defined waistline.
data.technique: Liposuction of the Abdomen and Bilateral Flanks

data.details: Quad blepharoplasty performed to rejuvenate the eyes by addressing both the upper and lower eyelids. This procedure removes excess skin and fat to improve eyelid contour, reduce puffiness, and create a more youthful, refreshed appearance.

Comprehensive face and neck lift performed using high SMAS flap technique for long-lasting lift and definition. Fat grafting to the midface was added to restore youthful volume and enhance facial contours.
data.technique: Face /Neck Lift with High SMAS Flaps and Autologous Fat Grafting to the Mid Face.

data.details: Mommy makeover including breast augmentation with implants and a tummy tuck to restore volume, tighten the abdomen, and enhance overall body contour.
Breast reduction performed to decrease volume, improve symmetry, and enhance overall breast shape and proportion.
Transaxillary breast augmentation using Mentor high profile implants 440cc on the right and 405cc on the left to achieve a fuller, symmetrical, and natural-looking result.
